00:48:25,447 --> 00:48:27,756
Odjednom je istrčala ispred mene.

548
00:48:58,807 --> 00:49:01,685
Nancy, dušo, jesi li dobro?

549
00:49:01,767 --> 00:49:03,917
videla sam ga! videla sam ga !

